description: Police detained the man after a "domestic incident" which left a 55-year-old woman in hospital.
title: Alderney attempted murder arrest over 'domestic incident'
title_page: Alderney attempted murder arrest over 'domestic incident' - BBC News
maintext: A 55-year-old woman was found injured and, after treatment at Le Mignot Hospital, was transferred to Guernsey where she is in a "stable condition" .
